text.tspan: Web app and database to create structured data lake
consisting of case studies accross the continent.
Goal is to help medical workers accross hospitals and nations
Accumulated data can also be analysed by big data researchers
to spot trends to generate hypothesis for clinical trials.
Focus is urgent care, and optimal treatmant identification.
We are creating a tool for rapid learning in time of crisis:
In the post-pandemic future the OECO
can improve agility and resiliance of European health sector
allowing through pooled and shared data rapid identification
of optimal treatmant strategies for new pathogen strains.
OECO - Open European Case study Observatory
